	<div id="id197b" class="post">
		<h2 class="title"><span class="image-wrapper"><img height="45" alt="Coiffure for cheapskates" width="280" class="title" src="../../../resources/net.databinder.components.RenderedLabel/7e4d0cf5"/><span class="title">Coiffure for cheapskates</span></span></h2>
		<div class="byline"><span>
			<span>By <span class="alias">Doctor Barnett</span>, <span>on February 15, 2006</span></span>
			<span id="id197c" class="tags">
					{&nbsp;<span><a href="../../../city/tag/shopping/#selected-tag"><span>shopping</span></a></span>&nbsp;}
			</span>
		</span></div>
		<div><p style="float:right"><img src="/pictures/barber.jpg" alt="" /></p>


	<p style="padding-top: 2.5em;">I’ve been meaning to write about my favorite barber shop for ages, but was waiting until I had a good picture of it.  Took one easily yesterday, cuz with the <a href="/doc/articles/2006/02/08/face-it-our-camera-rules">FZ-5</a> everybody can shoot like a V.P.</p>


	<p style="clear:right;">Do you…</p>


	<ul>
	<li>Want to spend less than $20 on a hair cut?</li>
		<li>Want to see the same stylist every cut?</li>
		<li>Live or work near Houston and Broadway?</li>
	</ul>


	<p>Ok, you two New Yorkers, <em>this is the barbershop of your dreams!</em></p>


	<p>As you can see it’s at <strong>641 Broadway (phone: 212 777-2899)</strong> which is on the block above Houston, West side. It is not normally barricaded by garbage, but we did just have the greatest recorded snowfall in history, folks.</p>


	<p><a href="/eat">MrLittlePants</a> and I always see <strong>Elise</strong> who does great work (come on, you’re familiar with my perfect <em>bouffant</em>), but I’ve also had my hair cut by the blond Eastern European woman and she did a fine job, silently.</p>


	<p>If you walk in and they aren’t busy, someone will whisk you right into a chair unless you stop them, or if you’re a babbling street person or something. In that case they will probably not whisk you into a chair.</p>


	<p>Happy chopping, you nasty long-haired beast!</p></div>
